Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:23.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君と僕の仲で何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:33.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}キメキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:39.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:34.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}給予了我所度過的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:43.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}必須在這裡刻下心靈吼叫的那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:52.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}強忍著淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:54.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:58.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}連夢想也與我無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:04.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}看著天空一句話也說不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:12.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直思考著胸口的那股痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:14.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
